            <fr:title text="Baby steps in higher domain theory › Is the partial map classifier a Sierpiński cone? (V)"><fr:link href="/jms-00RN/" title="Baby steps in higher domain theory" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00RN/" display-uri="jms-00RN" type="local">Baby steps in higher domain theory</fr:link> › Is the partial map classifier a Sierpiński cone? (V)</fr:title>
